---
---

<section class="features" id="features">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="section-head fade-in">
      <p class="eyebrow">Why Loggie</p>
      <h2>Built for people who do a lot.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid">

      <div class="feat-card fade-in" style="background:#C5E0BC; transition-delay:0ms">
        <svg class="icon" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M12 2L3 7V13C3 17.55 7.16 21.74 12 23C16.84 21.74 21 17.55 21 13V7L12 2Z" stroke="#1D2025" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <path d="M9 12L11 14L15 10" stroke="#1D2025" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        <h3>Completely private</h3>
        <p>All data stays on your device. No cloud, no servers — your activity stays yours forever.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feat-card fade-in" style="background:#CDBCE6; transition-delay:80ms">
        <svg class="icon" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M12 3L13.5 7.5L18 9L13.5 10.5L12 15L10.5 10.5L6 9L10.5 7.5L12 3Z" stroke="#1D2025" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <path d="M6 17L6.75 19.25L9 20L6.75 20.75L6 23L5.25 20.75L3 20L5.25 19.25L6 17Z" stroke="#1D2025" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        <h3>AI&#8209;powered recall</h3>
        <p>Ask any LLM what you were working on, find lost tabs, or summarise your week. Context that actually works.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feat-card fade-in" style="background:#ffffff; transition-delay:160ms">
        <svg class="icon" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <rect x="3" y="3" width="8" height="8" rx="1.5" stroke="#1D2025" stroke-width="1.6"/>
          <rect x="13" y="3" width="8" height="8" rx="1.5" stroke="#1D2025" stroke-width="1.6"/>
          <rect x="3" y="13" width="8" height="8" rx="1.5" stroke="#1D2025" stroke-width="1.6"/>
          <rect x="13" y="13" width="8" height="8" rx="1.5" stroke="#1D2025" stroke-width="1.6"/>
        </svg>
        <h3>Every app, every tab</h3>
        <p>Active windows, browser tabs, documents, meeting titles — Loggie captures the full context of your workday.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feat-card fade-in" style="background:#FFDFC2; transition-delay:240ms">
        <svg class="icon" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 000-7.78z" stroke="#1D2025" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        <h3>Silent &amp; lightweight</h3>
        <p>Runs quietly in your menu bar with minimal resource usage. You won't even notice it's there.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features {
    padding: 7rem 2.5rem 6rem;
    background: #F0EDE4;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 64rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .section-head { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.625rem; }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: #9B9EA6;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.875rem, 3.5vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: #1D2025;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .feat-card {
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.875rem;
    min-height: 240px;
  }

  .icon { flex-shrink: 0; }

  .feat-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #1D2025;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  .feat-card p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(29,32,37,0.65);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .features { padding: 5rem 1.5rem 4rem; }
    .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .feat-card { min-height: auto; }
  }
</style>
